00:22:06.569 --> 00:22:20.839
and all their efforts. When the song started, 50,000 were in place here.

00:22:21.079 --> 00:22:26.359
And it was our proof that all the hard work and preparation was successful. And actually,

00:22:26.359 --> 00:22:34.460
I shared a tear of joy I did. One of the managers at the arena said, you have to stand and listen

00:22:34.460 --> 00:22:41.099
to the song, because you will never again hear a choir of 50,000 singing at the same time.

00:22:42.299 --> 00:22:55.930
You just have to listen to it. First, I want to thank you for how well it worked out.

00:22:56.650 --> 00:23:03.130
Normally, at the arrangements of this size, we are using an event agency. But you've done this

00:23:03.130 --> 00:23:10.089
