00:23:48.230 --> 00:23:52.309
I looked at the number of hotel bookings, and there are not many rooms available.

00:23:53.349 --> 00:23:57.829
There are many who can learn from the work of the logistics of how to get 50,000 people

00:23:57.829 --> 00:24:02.069
into the area at the same time. That is something we can learn a lot from.

