00:40:17.699 --> 00:40:22.099
with the construction overseer on the island. And he said, I've got really good news.

00:40:23.059 --> 00:40:27.940
There was no damage. The storm took a turn just before it hit the island and just grazed it.

00:40:28.900 --> 00:40:34.179
He says, I have some other good news. I just got a haul from the village chiefs.

00:40:35.380 --> 00:40:41.300
Apparently the storm surge had washed up a bunch of sand over their road to their villages

00:40:41.940 --> 00:40:47.380
and they had no way of removing it. So they said, we have plenty of sand. Can you come and help us

00:40:47.380 --> 00:40:52.260
get rid of it? So we ended up having enough sand for the rest of the project.

