00:51:32.599 --> 00:51:40.599
the branch broke, I fell to the ground, and I was paralyzed. At that moment, I went from an

00:51:40.599 --> 00:51:48.039
active kid who could run to one who was paralyzed from his neck down. I couldn't feel anything.

00:51:48.440 --> 00:51:56.599
