00:51:56.599 --> 00:52:06.840
independence. At that point, I attended a university and lived on campus. My life changed dramatically

00:52:06.840 --> 00:52:16.599
once again. Here I was exposed to drugs, alcohol, immorality, and I fell into that lifestyle.

00:52:17.559 --> 00:52:23.960
Every night, though, I still read the Bible. I still had this strong faith in God.

00:52:25.000 --> 00:52:31.639
But, when I prayed and went to sleep at night, I just knew I was going to end up in that

00:52:31.639 --> 00:52:41.530
hellfire that I had been taught from an early age. During this time, I met a girl named Julie,

00:52:41.530 --> 00:52:48.489
and we were married shortly after. She was in the same hippie lifestyle that I was in,

00:52:48.969 --> 00:52:54.409
and we knew if we were going to stay married, we had to move away from our bad influence.

00:52:55.449 --> 00:53:02.650
We were looking for God, and we wanted Him in our life. One day, I was in the park by myself.

00:53:03.369 --> 00:53:08.730
